text: Kelechukwu Rowland Okereke (born 13 October 1981), known as Kele Okereke, is a British singer and guitarist for rock band Bloc Party. He was born in Liverpool on 13 October 1981 and grew up in London, England, United Kingdom. His parents are from Nigeria.
